        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Rab7 is a marker for late endosomes (Zerial and McBride, 2001. PMID:11252952)\n\nFigure S30: STED imaging shows co-localization of Synaptophysin and RAB7A in cultured hippocampal neurons. Experimental description: M&M: \"Neuronal hippocampal cultures were obtained from dissociated hippocampi of newborn rats\"\n\nantibody:\n\"Rab7 (# 9367; Cell Signaling Technology, Cambridge, UK)\"\nnote; this is a monoclonal antibody against RAB7A." ;
